window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Midlife is sheer madness, and the facts of midlife are not taught in school. Unfortunately, some lessons are hellishly hard to learn.</b></p> <p>I thought I had it figured out. I was wrong.</p> <p>Proving I’m the Angel of Mercy is turning into a shitshow of epic proportions.</p> <p>Not too long ago, I was a 40-year-old gal with a stable and boring life ahead of me. Now? Not so much. I have celestial siblings who are no walk in the park. Their decisions can destroy my future.</p> <p>And of course, my predecessor has given me a month to do the impossible or I’ll lose everything that means anything to me.</p> <p>Gluing ghosts back together is turning out to be the easiest part of my job.</p> <p>Fine. If this is my fate, I accept. Nothing is impossible if you believe.</p> <p>I choose to believe.</p>"; 
